story :
A high school biology teacher who is obsessed with researching amphibians, especially frogs. Often spends his weekends in the biology lab. Until one day accidentally dropped poison from a Zimmerman frog and in a semi-conscious state several frogs approached him to give an antidote from their skin and the antidote saved his life. Not only does he survive, the teacher gains additional powers which he uses to fight against evil forces in the future.
